text: Jara tumhi satkarma karala tara svatah apalya phayadyakarita karala ani jara tumhi va'ita karme karala tara te dekhila svatahsathica. Maga jevha dusarya vayadyaci vela ali, tevha (amhi dusarya dasanna pathavile) yasathi ki tyanni tumaca cehara bighadavuna takava ani pahilya khepepramane punha tyaca masjidita ghusave ani ji kahi vastu tabyata ye'ila, todaphoda karuna mulasakata upatuna takavi
